basketball /ˈbɑːskɪtˌbɔːl, ˈbæs-/

(basketballs) 

1. N-UNCOUNT Basketball is a game in which two teams of five players each try to score goals by throwing a large ball through a circular net fixed to a metal ring at each end of the court. 篮球运动 

2. N-COUNT A basketball is a large ball which is used in the game of basketball. 篮球

